com.github.fge.grappa.run

Interface ParseRunner<V>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractParseRunner, ListeningParseRunner

    public interface ParseRunner<V>
    A ParseRunner performs the actual parsing run of a given parser rule on a given input text.

    Note: if you want to use a parser on a String input, use the run(CharSequence) method, since String implements CharSequence (and so does CharBuffer; see also for large files).
